                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-221-off1224 t18300415-221-cd1225"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-221-victim1942" type="victimName">
                           Alexander Bailey 
